alarm_decription: Alarm that monitors vSphere Log File System Resource Exhaustion. (vcenter01.njwc.com)

alarm_name: vSphere Health detected new issues in your environment
alarm_decription: This alarm is fired when vSphere Health detects new issues in your environment. This alarm will be retriggered even if acknowledged when new issues are detected. Go to Monitor -> Health for a detailed description of the issues.

alarm_name: Skyline Health has detected issues in your vSphere environment
alarm_decription: This alarm is fired when vSphere Health detects new issues in your environment. This alarm will be retriggered even if acknowledged when new issues are detected. Go to Monitor -> Health for a detailed description of the issues.
